title: YouChannell 2012-2013 Chapter Six Illustrations
body:
Hey guys, I’ve been working on this series for approximately two years now (in book form at least). Here are all of the pictures for Chapter Six.

This chapter deals with menstruation and birthday.

YouChannell: 2012-2013 is a slice-of-life realistic fiction story of sixteen tweens and teenagers living in a group home in northeast Portland, Oregon, United States. Be it the transfer to public school, a kickball match, crushes on girls, a new kid in the house, and much much more, YouChannell: 2012-2013 is sure to either make you chuckle, cry like a little bitch, or just stare at the computer screen for hours.

Go on, check it out if you like, and I hope you enjoy: https://manicthemod.wordpress.com/2018/12/03/youchannell-2012-2013-chapter-six-fourteen-is-one-bloody-hell-of-an-age-june-23-2012-800-a-m/

Guys, it would mean the whole world to me if at least one person clicked on the link and read!! And also, thank you so much for clicking on this piece!!
